# stock-price-prediction-lstm
This project predicts stock price trends using LSTM deep learning models. Historical data is collected from Yahoo Finance and processed with technical indicators like Moving Average and RSI. The system visualizes actual vs predicted prices to help analyze stock market trends.
Overview

This project predicts stock price trends using Long Short-Term Memory (LSTM) neural networks. Historical stock data is collected from Yahoo Finance, preprocessed, and used to train a deep learning model that forecasts future price movements and visualizes actual vs predicted trends.

Objectives

Collect historical stock price data

Preprocess and normalize time-series data

Build and train an LSTM-based deep learning model

Predict future stock price trends

Visualize actual vs predicted stock prices

