 Methodology

Data Collection ‚Äì Fetch historical stock data using Yahoo Finance

Preprocessing ‚Äì Handle missing values and normalize data

Feature Engineering ‚Äì Use technical indicators like Moving Average and RSI

Model Building ‚Äì LSTM neural network with dropout layers

Training ‚Äì Train model using historical data

Prediction ‚Äì Forecast stock price trends

Visualization ‚Äì Plot actual vs predicted prices

 How to Run (Google Colab)

Open Google Colab

Upload stock_prediction.ipynb

Run all cells sequentially

The model will train and display prediction graphs

Saved model file: lstm_stock_model.keras

Results

The LSTM model learns historical price patterns and predicts future trends with good accuracy. The prediction curve closely follows actual stock prices, demonstrating effective time-series learning.

 Limitations

Market volatility affects prediction accuracy

External factors like news and sentiment are not considered

Best suited for trend prediction, not exact prices

 Future Scope

Integrate news and sentiment analysis

Deploy using Streamlit web dashboard

Add more technical indicators

Extend to cryptocurrency and forex markets

